<doc id="147886" wikidata="Q7252579" url="?curid=147886" title="Taiwan Province (disambiguation)">
<text>[[Taiwan Province]] is a nominal administrative division of Taiwan.

Taiwan Province, or Province of Taiwan, may also refer to:
* Taiwan Province, People&#x27;s Republic of China, a nominal administrative division claimed, but never controlled, by China
* Taiwan under Japanese rule, when Taiwan was an administrative division of the Empire of Japan
* Taiwan under Qing rule, when Taiwan was an administrative division of the Great Qing

